If depth = 0
→ Return value of Tree

If player = MAX
2.1 Set bestValue ← −∞
2.2 For each child of Tree
  a. value ← Alpha–Beta Pruning(child, depth − 1, α, β, MIN)
  b. bestValue ← max(bestValue, value)
  c. α ← max(α, value)
  d. If β ≤ α
    → Break (Beta cut-off)
2.3 Return bestValue

Else (player = MIN)
3.1 Set bestValue ← +∞
3.2 For each child of Tree
  a. value ← Alpha–Beta Pruning(child, depth − 1, α, β, MAX)
  b. bestValue ← min(bestValue, value)
  c. β ← min(β, value)
  d. If β ≤ α
    → Break (Alpha cut-off)
3.3 Return bestValue

End
